361
00:23:39,710 --> 00:23:41,771
Obviously.

362
00:23:41,796 --> 00:23:44,257
But Kanga-man
is definitely a man.

363
00:23:44,382 --> 00:23:47,068
He's the result

364
00:23:47,093 --> 00:23:48,986
of an unsuccessful experiment.

365
00:23:49,012 --> 00:23:50,030
It wasn't that unsuccessful.

366
00:23:50,054 --> 00:23:54,017
It has good legs,
and a good ass.

367
00:23:54,058 --> 00:23:58,604
An this?
What's this?

368
00:23:58,729 --> 00:24:00,982
That's an R
for Retarder.

369
00:24:01,107 --> 00:24:02,666
No, not for Retarder.

370
00:24:02,692 --> 00:24:05,336
Rewindo.

371
00:24:05,362 --> 00:24:08,156
He can make
everything go in reverse.

372
00:24:08,281 --> 00:24:10,258
He walks backwards.

373
00:24:10,283 --> 00:24:12,343
Does he travel in time?

374
00:24:12,369 --> 00:24:14,787
No, no, no.
He just walks backwards.

375
00:24:14,912 --> 00:24:16,497
No.
- Yes.

376
00:24:16,622 --> 00:24:18,291
- Is that a superpower?
- Of course!

377
00:24:18,416 --> 00:24:20,477
He does it really fast.

378
00:24:20,501 --> 00:24:22,019
Okay.

379
00:24:22,045 --> 00:24:23,546
Imagine he's walking
down the street

380
00:24:23,671 --> 00:24:25,423
