with a knife.

381
00:24:25,548 --> 00:24:27,967
The man walks backwards
away from him.

382
00:24:28,092 --> 00:24:29,344
It's really easy to escape,
do you understand?

383
00:24:29,468 --> 00:24:32,222
Sure, yes. Why not?
If you say so.

384
00:24:32,347 --> 00:24:35,825
I draw all of these

385
