386
00:24:39,312 --> 00:24:41,398
But all of them
look like you.

387
00:24:41,522 --> 00:24:45,402
- What?
- Yes, they're cute.

388
00:24:45,526 --> 00:24:46,986
They all remind me
of you.

389
00:24:47,111 --> 00:24:50,089
