- What's that?

395
00:25:04,170 --> 00:25:05,922
- What?
- Is that your door or mine?

396
00:25:06,047 --> 00:25:07,731
I don't know.

397
00:25:07,757 --> 00:25:10,968
It's mine.
- What are you doing?

398
00:25:11,094 --> 00:25:12,529
I have to go.

399
00:25:12,553 --> 00:25:14,597
Why?
Where are you going, Juana?

400
00:25:14,722 --> 00:25:16,699
What are you doing?

401
00:25:21,729 --> 00:25:24,707
Juana! Juana!

402
00:25:36,660 --> 00:25:39,096
