408
00:25:50,216 --> 00:25:51,692
Sure.

409
00:25:51,717 --> 00:25:53,110
I have the afternoon free.

410
00:25:53,136 --> 00:25:54,529
I'd like you to join me.

411
00:25:54,553 --> 00:25:56,306
Let's have something
to eat.

412
00:25:56,431 --> 00:25:58,057
Yes, yes, yes.
Sure. Let's go.

413
00:25:58,182 --> 00:25:59,867
