A hamburger?

416
00:26:03,687 --> 00:26:05,164
What do you want?

417
00:26:05,189 --> 00:26:06,399
Yes, yes.
A buffalo burger.

418
00:26:06,524 --> 00:26:09,502
Hi! Is this your father?

419
00:26:09,527 --> 00:26:11,028
- Diego.
- Jose.

420
00:26:11,154 --> 00:26:14,131
He's the new tenant.

421
00:26:17,034 --> 00:26:19,970
Did you need something?

422
00:26:22,039 --> 00:26:24,625
- No.
- Shall we go?

423
00:26:24,750 --> 00:26:27,504
- Yes. Excuse me.
- Nice to meet you.

424
00:26:37,763 --> 00:26:40,517
- Dad, are you there?
- Yes! I'm down here.

425
00:26:46,481 --> 00:26:48,358
- Hello.
- Hello!

426
00:26:48,483 --> 00:26:50,167
You're home early.

427
00:26:50,193 --> 00:26:52,545
No.

428
00:26:52,570 --> 00:26:55,072
A new heater,
isn't it?

429
00:26:55,198 --> 00:26:57,992
Finally, hot water.
No more toxic waste.

430
00:26:58,117 --> 00:27:00,094
It was about time.

431
00:27:00,119 --> 00:27:02,012
We'll finally have hot water

432
00:27:02,038 --> 00:27:04,265
whenever we want to!

433
00:27:04,290 --> 00:27:05,624
So what?
Shall we try it?

434
00:27:05,749 --> 00:27:07,226
Sure!

435
00:27:07,251 --> 00:27:10,854
Okay. I'm coming.

436
00:27:07,251 --> 00:27:08,811
Go to the kitchen.

437
00:27:10,880 --> 00:27:12,773
Open the kitchen faucet.

438
00:27:12,798 --> 00:27:14,317
Yes, yes.

439
00:27:14,342 --> 00:27:18,762
Let me know
when there's water running.

440
00:27:18,888 --> 00:27:21,182
- Ready?
- Ready!

441
00:27:21,307 --> 00:27:26,103
- Okay!
- It's open!

442
00:27:26,229 --> 00:27:28,247
Coming!

443
00:27:34,362 --> 00:27:37,532
It's 117,000 BTU,
corrosion resistant,

444
00:27:37,656 --> 00:27:40,451
draught reducer,
automatic pilot.

445
00:27:40,577 --> 00:27:42,052
Wonderful!

446
00:27:42,078 --> 00:27:46,098
It also saves energy.

447
00:27:46,123 --> 00:27:49,043
What are you doing?
Be careful.

448
00:27:49,168 --> 00:27:51,212
- Did you burn?
- No, dad. I'm fine.

449
00:27:51,337 --> 00:27:53,172
- Are you sure?
- Yes, I'm fine.

450
00:27:53,297 --> 00:27:56,133
We have to adjust
temperature.

451
00:28:02,306 --> 00:28:05,142
Junior, about
yesterday,

452
00:28:05,268 --> 00:28:06,827
I'd like to--

453
00:28:06,852 --> 00:28:08,871
Er, dad.

454
00:28:08,896 --> 00:28:12,041
Dad, I'm sorry about the pool.

455
00:28:14,151 --> 00:28:19,156
No, not at all.
It isn't your fault.

456
00:28:19,282 --> 00:28:25,680
It was my fault.

457
00:28:25,704 --> 00:28:28,165
Your old man
embarrassed himself.

458
00:28:28,291 --> 00:28:30,209
I'd like you to
know

459
00:28:30,334 --> 00:28:33,170
that I'm not proud
of my behavior.

460
00:28:33,296 --> 00:28:35,856
Just the opposite.

461
00:28:35,881 --> 00:28:39,527
I feel very foolish.

462
00:28:39,552 --> 00:28:42,096
Henry and you
seemed pissed off.

463
00:28:42,221 --> 00:28:44,641
No, it's okay.
Everything is fine.

464
00:28:44,765 --> 00:28:46,200
We're fine.

465
00:28:46,225 --> 00:28:48,102
I called him
to apologize.

466
00:28:48,227 --> 00:28:51,063
I owe you an apology
most of all.

467
00:28:51,188 --> 00:28:53,483
What I did was
terrible.

468
00:28:53,608 --> 00:28:59,363
Forcing you to drink
was very bad.

469
00:28:59,489 --> 00:29:03,133
I'm really sorry.

470
00:29:03,159 --> 00:29:05,553
But I did it okay, didn't I?

471
00:29:05,578 --> 00:29:07,722
Because I kept up with you.

472
00:29:07,746 --> 00:29:10,541
I had almost
as much tequila as you.

473
00:29:15,963 --> 00:29:18,757
Er... I have some
tools to put away.

474
00:30:46,970 --> 00:30:50,407
- Hello.

475
00:30:50,433 --> 00:30:52,535
