476
00:30:52,560 --> 00:30:56,038
Hey.

477
00:30:56,063 --> 00:31:04,154
- What?

478
00:30:56,063 --> 00:31:00,292
- Explain it.

479
00:31:00,317 --> 00:31:04,254
- About your father.

480
00:31:04,280 --> 00:31:05,631
There's nothing to explain.

481
00:31:05,656 --> 00:31:06,907
- Really?
- No.

482
00:31:07,032 --> 00:31:08,467
So what?

483
00:31:08,492 --> 00:31:10,135
I misread your attitude.

484
00:31:10,160 --> 00:31:12,054
I was doing you a favor.

485
00:31:12,079 --> 00:31:13,472
A favor? Really?

486
00:31:13,497 --> 00:31:15,683
My father is an ogre.

487
00:31:15,708 --> 00:31:17,852
He seemed cool to me.

488
00:31:17,876 --> 00:31:19,478
It's all yours.

489
00:31:19,503 --> 00:31:21,146
What happened, Juana?

490
00:31:21,171 --> 00:31:23,382
I was protecting you,
okay?

491
00:31:23,507 --> 00:31:26,652
How's that?

492
00:31:26,677 --> 00:31:28,429
I let you smoke in here.
Do you remember it?

493
00:31:28,554 --> 00:31:30,489
I bought a filter,

494
00:31:30,514 --> 00:31:32,449
my lady.

495
00:31:32,475 --> 00:31:34,685
The less my father knows,
the better.

496
00:31:34,811 --> 00:31:36,787
Juana, you acted

497
00:31:36,813 --> 00:31:39,707
